#

Tofu Wraps with Hummus

15 min
$10
200 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

SoySesame (if using tahini in hummus)

Dietary Tags:

VeganVegetarianGluten-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

QuickHealthyLunchSnack

Description

A delicious and healthy wrap filled with protein-packed tofu and creamy hummus, perfect for a quick lunch or snack!

Ingredients

  • firm tofu: 1 block (14 oz)
  • hummus: 1/2 cup
  • whole wheat tortillas: 4
  • spinach leaves: 1 cup
  • bell pepper: 1 (sliced)
  • cucumber: 1 (sliced)
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
